<header class="article-header">
	<p class="article-date"><time datetime="2015-04-27T21:00:45+09:00" itemprop="datePublished">2015年04月27日</time></p>
	<h1 class="article-title" itemprop="name"><a href="http://doonroom.blog.jp/archives/32142654.html" itemprop="url">Gazing Kiss</a></h1>
	
</header>
